---item_30 Refined Wyld Luck---
Type :: Usable
Icon :: items_647
Slot :: Item
Rarity :: Exotic
Max Stacks :: 99

Use this item to get another loot box from the boss you just killed. Must be used quickly after the boss dies or will not function. Can be used in Corrupted Dungeons up to Level 10.

It takes a single craftsman nearly a month just to make one of these. Use them wisely.